1
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:35,960
Be careful.

2
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:46,280
Cui Linlang.

3
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:50,890
Cui Linlang.

4
00:01:58,320 --> 00:02:00,160
The Northern border defense map

5
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:08,199
is my wedding gift to you.

6
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,440
You took my blade,

7
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:14,970
and I give you a gift.

8
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:18,720
From now on, we are even.

9
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:24,520
Father.

10
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:27,560
I have

11
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:30,000
avenged you.

12
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:33,970
Cui Linlang.

13
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:10,960
Step up.

14
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:19,440
Second Miss, Mr. Su has arrived.

15
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:22,160
I am fortunate you let me stay the night.

16
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,890
I came especially to thank you.

17
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:26,440
I happened to obtain a guqin.

18
00:03:27,079 --> 00:03:28,640
Its sound is clear and pure.

19
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,280
I believe in this world,

20
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:32,640
only someone as elegant as you, Second Miss,

21
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:33,840
can truly match it.

22
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,850
Though I am untalented,

23
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,810
I wish to present this guqin to you.

24
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:40,520
I'd also be so bold as to ask you to play a piece.

25
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:42,050
Your generous gift, Mr. Su,

26
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,000
is too much for me.

27
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:47,400
Since it's a fine guqin, how can I refuse?

28
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:53,920
What is that sound?

29
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:54,920
Madam,

30
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:56,520
it's the Second Miss

31
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:59,400
and our guest, Young Master Su from Southern Xinjiang.

32
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,800
They seem to be playing a duet.

33
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,800
Young Master Su is very elegant.

34
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:06,040
He and the Second Miss look like a good match.

35
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:08,500
He is a shady person from Southern Xinjiang.

36
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,980
How could she bring him into our mansion?

37
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:14,040
No, I must go and see.

38
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,800
Madam, please do not get angry.

39
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,720
Step aside.

40
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:20,620
Your health is important, Madam.

41
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:51,340
Young Master Su's flute music

42
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,159
is deep and resonant,

43
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,330
touching the heart.

44
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:57,560
It seems to hide many untold

45
00:04:58,200 --> 00:04:59,040
sorrows.

46
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,800
Life is like walking at night.

47
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,280
Though the eyes cannot see the frosty moon,

48
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,940
the heart yearns for clarity.

49
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:09,040
I have wandered for half my life.

50
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:11,400
All I seek is a kindred spirit.

51
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:14,040
To spend the rest of our lives together

52
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:14,960
is enough.

53
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,080
Mr. Su, why put yourself down?

54
00:05:18,080 --> 00:05:19,040
In this world,

55
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:23,400
there are many who can see clearly, but their hearts are as blind as the night.

56
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:26,400
They are not as clear-hearted

57
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,860
and perceptive as you.

58
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:30,160
Your words,

59
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:32,360
miss, seem to imply

60
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,420
you have a lot on your mind too.

61
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,080
Could it be

62
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:39,530
you still haven't forgotten that old friend?

63
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:43,200
The past

64
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,720
cannot be chased.

65
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:47,000
Why don't you look

66
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:49,240
at the person in front of you?

67
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:17,800
You're awake.

68
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:22,930
Now you really have to marry me.

69
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:26,480
You've seen and touched every inch

70
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:28,760
of my body, inside and out.

71
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:36,560
Doctors see no gender.

72
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:38,680
There are only patients.

73
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:41,520
Don't think you can blackmail me with this.

74
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,000
My legs.

75
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:51,760
Cui Linlang's stab injured your back.

76
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,480
Your legs will feel numb.

77
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:56,690
I'll clear your meridians for you.

78
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:58,300
Is it numb here?

79
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,540
Does it feel uncomfortable here?

80
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,490
How is your back?

81
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:04,900
Let me check your back.

82
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:11,400
I want to kiss you.

83
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,440
Don't move.

84
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:35,419
Once our families are cleared of false charges,

85
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:37,780
I will marry you, okay?

86
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:09,360
The Khan is in a great mood lately.

87
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:12,200
Dafeng came to seek peace

88
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,800
and offered generous gifts.

89
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:16,720
He is naturally happy.

90
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:20,080
What generous gifts?

91
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:23,000
That's ceding territory for peace.

92
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:25,040
The Emperor of Dafeng doing this

93
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:28,960
is simply humiliating the country.

94
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:43,400
Young man.

95
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,780
You understand our language.

96
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,640
You must be joking.

97
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:49,840
I can barely understand the official language.

98
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:52,100
How could I understand a foreign tongue?

99
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:01,300
The Han people have an old saying.

100
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,720
Better to kill by mistake

101
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,640
than to let one slip away.

102
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:35,450
Someone is dead!

103
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,560
Someone is dead!

104
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:40,720
Run!

105
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:12,840
Who is it?

106
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,240
They are Beidi.

107
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:17,600
They mumbled a bunch of things,

108
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,200
and then

109
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:21,200
threw Xiao Wu

110
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,280
down from upstairs.

111
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:41,220
The past is beyond recall.

112
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:45,040
Why not look at the person in front of you?

113
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:06,960
Second Miss, Mr. Su asks to see you.

114
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:27,480
Mr. Su, you're visiting late at night.

115
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:28,600
What is the matter?

116
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:31,450
I just passed by the courtyard,

117
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,860
heard your melancholy lute playing,

118
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,860
and came following the sound.

119
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:38,240
I have some heartfelt words

120
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:40,440
that have been on my mind for a long time.

121
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:42,520
If I don't say them today,

122
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:45,040
I'm afraid I will regret it forever.

123
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:47,160
Go ahead.

124
00:12:48,160 --> 00:12:50,480
Although I am blind,

125
00:12:50,680 --> 00:12:52,010
I have feelings for you.

126
00:12:52,920 --> 00:12:55,800
If you'll have me, I'm willing to marry into the Yan family,

127
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:57,560
share your burdens, manage the household,

128
00:12:57,560 --> 00:13:01,360
and stay with you for the rest of my life.

129
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,320
Young Master Su,

130
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:22,440
do you really mean it?

131
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:23,890
If I break this oath,

132
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,650
may gods and men forsake me.

133
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:27,800
Mingli,

134
00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:29,380
if you are willing,

135
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:32,240
we can hold our wedding ceremony tonight.

136
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:33,860
What do you say?

137
00:13:48,680 --> 00:13:50,280
Second Miss, you have such a beautiful face.

138
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:54,010
This wedding dress will surely make you look like a heavenly fairy.

139
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,920
We are finally married.

140
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:06,810
May this heart and this mind

141
00:14:07,640 --> 00:14:09,000
never be let down.

142
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:13,800
Why does it have to be now?

143
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:18,440
Jingyan.

144
00:15:20,560 --> 00:15:23,760
I want to stay with you until the clouds part and the sun shines,

145
00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:27,960
and see the grievances of the Xiao and Yan families cleared with my own eyes.

146
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:28,760
But I

147
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:32,480
seem unable to live to see that day.

148
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:42,500
Aunt Qin's ancient medical books

149
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:45,000
might hold a glimmer of hope.

150
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,800
Since Aunt Qin was murdered,

151
00:15:48,120 --> 00:15:49,840
the map to the Medicine King Valley

152
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:52,840
vanished from the world along with the medical books.

153
00:16:16,920 --> 00:16:17,480
Sir.

154
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:20,090
Everything went smoothly.

155
00:16:20,400 --> 00:16:22,130
She is convinced that I am Su Yan

156
00:16:23,040 --> 00:16:24,370
without any suspicion.

157
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:27,600
You took a steady first step,

158
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:31,120
gaining the identity of the Duke's son-in-law to help.

159
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:32,040
Next,

160
00:16:32,400 --> 00:16:34,130
we should take the second step.

161
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:38,000
The Duke had many disciples and old friends when he was alive.

162
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,130
Although rats abandon a sinking ship,

163
00:16:40,360 --> 00:16:42,520
there are still loyal and righteous people among them.

164
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:45,450
We need to secretly contact these old subordinates,

165
00:16:45,560 --> 00:16:47,880
unite them to petition the court,

166
00:16:48,560 --> 00:16:51,240
and clear the Duke's name.

167
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:52,880
Only in this way

168
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:54,300
can your Xie family

169
00:16:54,640 --> 00:16:56,920
have enough foundation to revive.

170
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:57,920
All right.

171
00:16:58,360 --> 00:16:59,040
Tomorrow,

172
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:01,040
I will use her name

173
00:17:02,280 --> 00:17:03,400
to act in secret.

174
00:17:03,920 --> 00:17:05,000
Be careful.

175
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:07,480
Don't let her get suspicious.

176
00:17:59,040 --> 00:17:59,880
Sister.

177
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:27,840
Cuimei.

178
00:18:29,080 --> 00:18:29,640
Yong.

179
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:31,840
Weikun, Huachao.

180
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:35,720
Long, Cong, Biao, Hao.

181
00:18:39,080 --> 00:18:39,680
Shuangbin.

182
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:40,640
Ningzheng.

183
00:18:43,040 --> 00:18:44,640
Hao, Chun, Kang, Shuai, Hua.

184
00:18:48,040 --> 00:18:48,570
Weichao.

185
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:49,210
Weichao.

186
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:51,360
Qiang, Yuan, Liang, Bo.

187
00:18:51,360 --> 00:18:52,690
Qiang, Yuan, Liang, Bo.

188
00:19:06,920 --> 00:19:07,280
Xi.

189
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:09,400
Xi.

190
00:19:09,480 --> 00:19:10,400
Tao, Qiang.

191
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:15,680
Hui, Yue, Yun, Qing.

192
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:19,680
Yiyi.

193
00:19:19,800 --> 00:19:20,280
Yiyi.
